definitions.definition: A city and civil parish with a city council in Cornwall , England ( OS grid ref SW8244 ) .

subdefinitions.definition: The Cornish constituency which existed from 1295 to 1997 and encompassed the city.

definitions.definition: A place in the United States :

subdefinitions.definition: A township and unincorporated community therein, in Knox County , Illinois .
A minor city in Madison County , Iowa .
A town in Barnstable County , Massachusetts .
A township in Franklin County , Ohio .

definitions.definition: A town in Colchester County , Nova Scotia , Canada .
A town in Mid Murray council area, South Australia .
